{"tid":602101,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"3香港啟動5CC載波聚合網速1.1Gbps　13.5GB片2分鐘Load完","createTime":"2018-03-22T18:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T17:05:38.000Z","uid":107023,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5c793bc109200ceaeb6eef64d16ff3160d86668e","tid":602101,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:18:58.000Z","msg":"3 香港今日（22/3）宣布啟動 5CC 載波聚合網絡技術，結合旗下 900 兆赫、1800 兆赫、2100 兆赫、2300 兆赫和 2600 兆赫五個頻段，提升網絡速度和覆蓋率。即是有多快？據他們資料顯示，透過 5CC 下載 2 小時的 4K Netflix 影片，假如網速可達 1.1 Gbps，最快 1 分 38 秒便完成。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n暫時只有 Samsung Galaxy S9/ S9+ 支援 5CC 載波聚合網絡技術<br />\n<br />\n3 香港解釋，載波聚合（Carrier Aggregation）技術可整合多個不同頻段的頻寬，提供更高頻寬和提升網速，令數據傳送更穩定和流暢；而 5CC（Component Carrier）載波聚合，就是以載波聚合技術結合 5 個 4G LTE 載波。<br />\n<br />\n他們又稱，3 香港是目前全港唯一以 900 兆赫、1800 兆赫、2100 兆赫、2300 兆赫和 2600 兆赫五個不同頻段的頻譜同時提供 4.5G 服務的營辦商，在去年已與華為部署將網絡升級至支援 5CC 載波聚合網絡技術，並加入了 4&times;4 MIMO 和 256 QAM 等技術，網絡測試最高速度可達 1.1 Gbps。<br />\n<br />\n根據他們提供的資料，假如 5CC 速度可達 1.1 Gbps，下載 2 小時的 4K Netflix 影片（13.5GB），最快 1 分 38 秒便完成；2 小時的 4K YouTube 影片（38.5GB）亦可在 4 分 40 秒內完成。不過，目前只有 Samsung Galaxy S9/ S9+ 支援 5CC 載波聚合網絡技術。<br />\n<br />\n3 香港資訊科技及流動電訊技術總裁鍾耀文表示，將來 5G 技術可為客戶和企業帶來無限商機，目前正與華為合作，並計劃在今年內啟用頻譜雲化（Cloud Air 2.0）技術，提升頻譜分配效率。華為方面亦指，雖然 5G 手機要待明年才有，但網絡需要先行。"},{"pid":"bc96cf212d247c907e3fed94aa84caf16ac84814","tid":602101,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"一秒1.1gbps, 得 S9/S9+ 先支援，但唔見samsung有sale呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a450aba1932f60e2cf427b52fbb0123122b3f233","tid":602101,"uid":113178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bc96cf212d247c907e3fed94aa84caf16ac84814","tid":602101,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"一秒1.1gbps, 得 S9/S9+ 先支援，但唔見samsung有sale呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"因為未有網絡供應商support?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4204813bbcc119ee2565e22a486580659b0ebca8","tid":602101,"uid":9193,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"幾十秒就用晒一個月quota了"},{"pid":"2eb3cd49ef31fc8aaa308ed7e87d4d7a63e0e551","tid":602101,"uid":16756,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4204813bbcc119ee2565e22a486580659b0ebca8","tid":602101,"uid":9193,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"幾十秒就用晒一個月quota了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T21:22:06.000Z","msg":"出得s9/s9+ 無錢玩真無限係咩玩法"},{"pid":"62b4e0c59287ebe79678bf0c62b1aa794f7f9cc7","tid":602101,"uid":177955,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"2eb3cd49ef31fc8aaa308ed7e87d4d7a63e0e551","tid":602101,"uid":16756,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4204813bbcc119ee2565e22a486580659b0ebca8","tid":602101,"uid":9193,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"幾十秒就用晒一個月quota了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T21:22:06.000Z","msg":"出得s9/s9+ 無錢玩真無限係咩玩法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T21:46:28.000Z","msg":"公平使用原則歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cccffca929138a8d74abf86e387c73d1ba0cf7","tid":602101,"uid":59946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a450aba1932f60e2cf427b52fbb0123122b3f233","tid":602101,"uid":113178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bc96cf212d247c907e3fed94aa84caf16ac84814","tid":602101,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"一秒1.1gbps, 得 S9/S9+ 先支援，但唔見samsung有sale呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"因為未有網絡供應商support?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,